				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I spent some hours in Vxed, and something strange occured :
<br />
an enchanter had a charmed mob. I had an air one. Even if I sent pet when mob at 60, he got aggro almost inmediatly and was hit. I tried to use a pet without weapon to aggro less, of course with Taunt off. But still pet got killed a lot if I /pet hold not fast enough.(and back off, yes, 'tis my standard macro).
<br />
First time I see that, but first time also in there.
<br />
strange, ain't it ? 
<br />

<br />

<br />
..
<br />
BTW, it is also the first time <span style="text-decoration: underline">I feel so useless</span>. Puller SK, Enchanter (quadding 900 pet) Cleric.  
<br />
3 others, doing almost nothing ! (oh, yes, a ranger was snaring) 3 /4 mobs I had not enough time to cast ONE  SV (even with BOR) and enchanter told me just to sinia pet when charm breaks (and it does a lot, even with all the right AAs, but our enchanter was a good player), and just wait for trial to be done. A wizz was also here, and she said same thing. 
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">boring</span> too bad, because some good loot dropping in there.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=159910">
