			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Agreed. 
<br />

<br />
Guys, it's simple. If there's more than 3 entities on a mob's hate list (charmed pet, you, plus one other), then the charmed pet WILL NOT hold aggro, ever. The mob will even go so far as to charge you even though you're not inside melee range to beat you down. The charmed pet Will not hold aggro, and it has absolutely nothing to do with aggro values, level or whatever of the other entities.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
